                                    Upper Back Lift procedures are often a careful balance between scarring and contour. While everyone’s goal is to maximize contour and minimize scarring, sometimes a trade off must exist. At The Oaks Plastic Surgery we take care to place the scar behind the brassiere. The surgeons at The Oaks Plastic Surgery want to work with you to achieve your specific goals.
